As a user, I want to be able to easily explore the gym’s facilities via the website before deciding if I want to become a member of the gym
As a user, I want to be able to easily sign up for a membership via the website, providing necessary personal details and selecting my preferred membership plan, so that I can quickly access the gym facilities and services.
As a user, I want to be able to view gym classes and select the one that suits my schedule 
As a user, I want to be able to receive personalized workout training from my trainers
As a user, I want to be able to learn more about the gym’s trainers and instructors, their professional backgrounds, certifications, experience and expertise  
